        "subject": "LU-2641 osd-ldiskfs: set dentry->d_sb for xattr calls",
        "message": "LU-2641 osd-ldiskfs: set dentry->d_sb for xattr calls\n\nCommit 431547b3 (v2.6.32) changed the generic xattr routines to\nuse dentry->d_sb instead of dentry->d_inode->i_sb.\n\nWe must set it before calling into the xattr routines that may be\nbacked by the generic ones, like ext4.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jeff Mahoney <jeffm@suse.com>\nChange-Id: I1064d2afd0d2bc10bbfff97e432f08d9e851b114\n"
      },
